Reclusa::

She had an indignant tone in her voice. "I am perfectly happy with my
own name thank you very much."  Then logic over ran her regal attitude
protocol programs. "BUt your right. I will need a new name. Hmm, what
about... " She tried not to choke as she let the name escape from her
vocal systems. "......Kestral."  She didn't like it, but it did sound
Maximal-ish. "Yes, Kestral, a small winged bird of prey. Smallest of
the hawks. Perhaps that might work."  She let her optics glance at
Perceptor. She wondered if he didn't feel sick to his metabolic
processors as much as she did. "Kestral. Kes for short."  She
shuttered. "Ick, well, let's hurry up and get this over with. The less
time I have to be a Maximush the better."
